     H            Y.
     F** UEXR04 ********************************************
     F*  EXSUB - GET PRE FROM PART                         *
     F*  J. WATANABE  2018.03.01                           *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UEXR04'
     F*                    PARM           $SHN   12
     F*                    PARM           $NOBN   20
     F*                    PARM           $NONY   40
     F*                    PARM           $QTY    80
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*  IN  $SHPDT  8 0 SHP DATE
     F*      $NOBN   2 0 BIN#
     F*      $NONY   4 0 DELIVERY CODE
     F*  OUT $QTY    8 0 TOTAL QTY
     F*      $RTN    1 A RETURN CODE (BKLANK=NO ERR, *=ERROR
     F******************************************************
     FAH#TL19 IF  E           K        DISK
     FALDPL30 IF  E           K        DISK
     FADAPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAGDPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAAIPL11 IF  E           K        DISK
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     E                    DT         24  1
     E                    BI         24  2 0
     E                    OBM        15  4               DEPT
     E                    OKB        15  3               MACHINE
     E                    OTK        15  6               LOCATION
     E                    OKO        15  3               PROCESS
      *
     I              '0123456789'          C         NUM
     I              '0123456789'          C         WKCKSU
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  24 DT
     I                                       01  01 CDDT08
     I                                       02  02 CDDT09
     I                                       03  03 CDDT10
     I                                       04  04 CDDT11
     I                                       05  05 CDDT12
     I                                       06  06 CDDT13
     I                                       07  07 CDDT14
     I                                       08  08 CDDT15
     I                                       09  09 CDDT16
     I                                       10  10 CDDT17
     I                                       11  11 CDDT18
     I                                       12  12 CDDT19
     I                                       13  13 CDDT20
     I                                       14  14 CDDT21
     I                                       15  15 CDDT22
     I                                       16  16 CDDT23
     I                                       17  17 CDDT24
     I                                       18  18 CDDT01
     I                                       19  19 CDDT02
     I                                       20  20 CDDT03
     I                                       21  21 CDDT04
     I                                       22  22 CDDT05
     I                                       23  23 CDDT06
     I                                       24  24 CDDT07
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  480BI
